ating the objectlocal eeb_editbox = gui.Editbox(eeb_gui, "eeb_editbox", "This is the text above the box");-- We are gonna keep track of the last text set herelocal cur_text = eeb_editbox:GetValue();-- Return Examplecallbacks.Register("Draw",function()-- Now to check if the text has changedif cur_text ~= eeb_editbox:GetValue() thencur_text = eeb_editbox:GetValue()eeb_editbox_TextChanged();endend);function eeb_editbox_TextChanged()-- We will now print the current text to the consoleprint(cur_text);endHow to set the text inside the box.eeb_editbox:SetValue("This will be in the box"); Table of contentsFunctionsentitiesFunctionsFindByClass(className)Find and put into table all entities with given class name.--Returns table of all playerslocal Players = entities.FindByClass("CCSPlayer");GetLocalPlayer()Return the local player entity.local LocalPlayer = entities.GetLocalPlayer();GetByIndex(index)Return the entity by index.local RandomPlayer = entities.GetByIndex(3);GetByUserID(userID)Return the entity by user idfor i = 1, globals.MaxClients(), 1 dolocal Player = entities.GetByUserID(i);endGetPlayerResources()Return the 'CCSPlayerResource' entitylocal playerResources = entities.GetPlayerResources();GetGameRules()Return the 'CCSGameRulesProxy' entitylocal gameRules = entities.GetGameRules(); Table of contentsFieldsFunctionsExampleClass: EntityFieldsThis class has no fields.Functionsstring GetName()Get the name of the entity.string GetModelName()Get the model name of the entity.string GetClass()Get the class of the entity.integer GetIndex()Get the entity index.integer GetTeamNumber()Vector3 GetAbsOrigin()Get the entity team number.Get the abs origin.Vector3 GetMins()Get mins of the entity.Vector3 GetMaxs()Get maxs of the entity.integer GetHealth()Get health of the entity.integer GetMaxHealth()boolean IsPlayer()boolean IsAlive()Get max health of the entity.Returns if the entity is a player.Returns if the entity is alive.boolean IsDormant()Returns if the entity is dormant.mixed